data.description: Under market value opportunity awaits! Beautiful area of Wellington Woods, where mature trees abound, surrounded by homes of great values. The home has been prepped for renovation for the next Owners, a canvas waiting to be finished. Brick w wood siding exterior for this 4BR 2.5BA two story home w two car attached garage.  Rosati windows have been installed. Main Level has a nice sized Living Room w WBFP & recessed lighting. The large Kitchen, w ceramic tile floors has newer cabinets, an eating space & a Family Room beside, sliding doors to the fenced backyard deck from there. There's also a Den/Office, Dining Room & Half BA. Four BRs up, Owner's BR/BA & 3 more good sized BRs w 2nd Full BA in Hallway. Full Finished Basement. Close to the River!
